{"title":"iphone safari不支持position fixed的解决办法","slug":"iphone-safari不支持position-fixed的解决办法","date":"2017-05-03T07:36:33.000Z","updated":"2017-05-03T07:38:01.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/iphone-safari不支持position-fixed的解决办法.json","excerpt":"","content":"<p>最近一直在做移动web开发，开发过程中遇到了许多问题，mobile safari不支持position: fixed或者对其支持不友好。</p>\n<p>废话不多说直接上代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div><div class=\"line\">5</div><div class=\"line\">6</div><div class=\"line\">7</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">&lt;div id=&quot;fixnav&quot; style=&quot; position: absolute; z-index: 1000; height: 50px; opacity: 0.9;&quot;&gt;nav&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class=\"line\">&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;</div><div class=\"line\">$(window).scroll(function()&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">     // 重点就是下面这一条语句的实现</div><div class=\"line\">     $(&quot;#fixnav&quot;).css(&#123;top: window.innerHeight + window.scrollY - $(&quot;#fixnav&quot;).outerHeight() &#125;);    </div><div class=\"line\"> &#125;);        </div><div class=\"line\">&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}